Directory Contact Tabs (Engine)
-------------------------------

This add-on for Mozilla Thunderbird 3 permits to fetch and display additional
information about contacts from LDAP directory servers.
It adds new panels (tabs) to contact info window.

The new panels are defined with XUL files provided by one or several customized "Directory Contact Tabs (Data)" add-ons.


This add-on is written in XUL and Javascript.

Trustedbird/Milimail project
